      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "customize",
          "data": {
            "data": {
              "parsed_content": [
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "人物關係",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 3,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 4914,
                      "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/01/02/237301566/fa4c986eefe97522566b35be6e29e7a0_471244222089785302.png",
                      "name": "Элинас",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "所有美露莘的「父親」。他曾經能夠與女兒們進行溝通，但美露莘卻再也沒辦法與「父親」溝通，唯獨瑪梅赫還能聽見「父親」的聲音。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "由於他非常喜愛他的女兒們，在他所創造的子空間內，化作了美露莘的模樣。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 4023,
                      "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/09/24/70239714/0513aa7f482dbb4778545d02f94956fe_5004007435087179259.png",
                      "name": "Нёвиллет",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "極力照顧美露莘的楓丹最高審判官。由他帶領美露莘到楓丹廷，並協助她們融入社會。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 4045,
                      "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/08/20/70239714/dd7d9c3c7e9285b9650a64fc6550622b_1437395977263774283.png",
                      "name": "Прорастающий протоген расщелин",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    },
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 4043,
                      "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/08/20/70239714/1317767095153c379837899e6c332db7_7324951828922334601.png",
                      "name": "Камнедробящий протоген расщелин",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    },
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 4044,
                      "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/08/20/70239714/622d9d846f1b800fa92b4c9c24ece5a7_2600000957143127249.png",
                      "name": "Большой прорастающий протоген расщелин",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    },
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 4042,
                      "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/08/20/70239714/d94d8c4feac0e0795a26552689d6689c_2170865110424809568.png",
                      "name": "Большой камнедробящий протоген расщелин",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "由厄里那斯創造的生命體，其目的是為了保護他的女兒們。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 4668,
                      "icon_url": "",
                      "name": "Pahsiv",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "看似美露莘與深海龍蜥的結合體的伊黎耶林區「精靈」。她的來歷與種類不明。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "著名的美露莘",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 3,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 4128,
                      "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/08/22/237301566/9cc2115edbfc809cdaa5a1629eb9dc37_9205678105566352048.png",
                      "name": "Мамер",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "一名藝術家，也是唯一能聽到「父親」聲音的美露莘。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 4916,
                      "icon_url": "",
                      "name": "Кэрол",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "其中一名被那維萊特帶入楓丹廷的美露莘。她成為了第一位加入逐影庭的美露莘。因為她的事蹟，執律庭的徽章上都以美露莘作為特色，以此表達對美露莘的尊敬和感激之情。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 4228,
                      "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/09/18/237301566/adba4f38203f23ea3cce8766735976f0_2706052043066089330.png",
                      "name": "Канотила",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "擁有與人類不一樣的世界認知的美露莘。她解讀了秘誨揭示之書。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 4354,
                      "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/09/20/237301566/165d4555e7265bfb02b2130be0a412bd_7099080460632654257.png",
                      "name": "Серин",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "海沫村的村長。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
